<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PetConnect — Page Not Found</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ base_path }}/Assets/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="centered-page">
    <div class="error-card">
        <div class="error-card__logo">PetConnect</div>

        <img
            src="{{ base_path }}/Assets/images/PetConnect-404-Error-Dog.png"
            alt="404 dog"
            class="error-card__img"
        >

        <span class="error-card__status">Page Not Found</span>

        <hr class="error-card__divider">

        <h1>Oops! We couldn't fetch that page.</h1>
        <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or may have been moved. Let's get you back to finding your new best friend.</p>

        <a href="{{ base_path }}/pets" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Browse Pets</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
